  ANSI, New York October 3, 2003 <strong>- </strong><em><a href="http://www.ansi.org/news_publications/news_story.aspx?menuid=7&articleid=516" target="_off">http://www.ansi.org/news_publications/news_story.aspx?menuid=7&amp;articleid=516 </a></em></p>
