              <p align="left" class="style2"><strong>Editorial</strong> :&nbsp; <a href="/bulletins/apr03.php#editorial">WHAT MAKES A &quot;GOOD&quot; STANDARD SETTING ORGANIZATION GOOD? </a><br>
  The modern technology-based world is increasingly dependent on the &quot;global standard setting infrastructure,&quot; made up of diverse processes and types of organizations. All are essential to the result and the value of each should be recognized and supported by Congress. </p>
